data.description: Welcome to the market 14095 Hwy 141! Are you looking for a home in the country with a lot of square footage? This is it! Best yet, this home is on pavement! There is a recently installed HVAC, a metal roof, and a finished Master with bath and walk-in closet located in the basement. The Sunroom is a very large space that is heated and cooled with a lot of big windows. There is a mud room off of the carport entry as well as a large pantry. There are 2 outbuildings, both have electric and one has water. This home is just oozing with potential. Call your favorite Realtor® to make this your home TODAY! Showings start Tuesday 9/5
